      "id": "cmr8hw7mt000cihc9xqxpths3",
      "url": "https://www.theberean.org/index.cfm/main/default/id/9272/leviticus-16-8.htm",
      "title": "Leviticus 16:8 - Unraveling Azazel: The True Meaning of the Scapegoat in Yom Kippur Rituals",
      "domain": "theberean.org",
